
See build64.sh for an example build script. 

Note: The currently the build system is only designed to support 
64 bit windows. 

For this to work the nvml.dll needs to be copied from 
C:\Program Files\NVIDIA Corporation\NVSMI into the 
C:\Windows\System32 directory as Java doesn't search this path when 
looking for libraries. The generated dll in 
builddir/src/.libs/libjnvml-0.dll also needs to be renamed to 
jnvml.dll and placed in the C:\Windows\System32 folder